{
  "texts": [
    "Before utilizing any pre-training corpus, it is suggested to review the specific terms and conditions of the applicable license to ensure compliance with relevant regulations.",
    "(3) The diversity of data types in pre-training corpora can impact the overall quality of LLMs.",
    "Models experience greater improvements when trained on corpora with a more diverse range of types.",
    "Hence, multi-category corpora are preferred, and they are the most numerous.",
    "Looking at singular data types, webpage data stands out as the most common in corpora due to its ease of access, large scale, and extensive content (as indicated in Figure 7 (c))."
  ]
}